---
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
import Separator from "../components/home/separator.astro";
---

<Layout title="Elvis Finol - Home">

    <section class="py-6 px-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-gray-200 via-gray-100 to-gray-50 shadow-md rounded-xl text-gray-700 text-left transition-all duration-300 ease-in-out space-y-5">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-left items-center gap-4">
            <!-- Heading -->
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold transform duration-300">
                <span>Hey there, <span class="text-orange-500">I'm Elvis! 👋🏻</span></span>
            </h1>
            
            <!-- Image -->
            <img 
                src="/assets/images/photo.png" 
                class="hidden sm:block rounded-full w-24 h-24 md:w-32 md:h-32 shadow-lg border-4 border-orange-400 hover:shadow-xl transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-105 object-cover" 
                alt="Elvis"
            />
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-auto">
            <h3 class="text-gray-700 text-lg">
                Senior System Engineer with diverse experience in problem-solving. Skilled in independent and team-based work across project lifecycles.
            </h3>
        </div>
        
        <div>
            <p class="font-semibold text-gray-600 dark:text-neutral-400">
                Based in Madrid 🇪🇸📍 
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-row justify-start gap-4">
            <a href="https://twitter.com/elvisfinol" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 bg-gray-200 text-black font-semibold rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-orange-400 transition duration-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M22.46 6c-.77.35-1.6.58-2.47.69a4.27 4.27 0 001.88-2.37 8.56 8.56 0 01-2.71 1.04A4.25 4.25 0 0011.91 9c0 .33.04.66.1.98A12.04 12.04 0 013 5.13a4.24 4.24 0 001.32 5.67 4.24 4.24 0 01-1.93-.54v.05a4.25 4.25 0 003.4 4.17 4.24 4.24 0 01-1.92.07 4.26 4.26 0 003.97 2.96A8.5 8.5 0 012 19.54a12.05 12.05 0 006.48 1.9c7.75 0 12-6.42 12-12V8.94A8.5 8.5 0 0022.46 6z"/>
                </svg>
            </a>
    
            <a href="https://www.instagram.com/elvisfinol.me/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 bg-gray-200 text-black font-semibold rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-orange-400 transition duration-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M15.233 5.488c-.843-.038-1.097-.046-3.233-.046s-2.389.008-3.232.046c-2.17.099-3.181 1.127-3.279 3.279-.039.844-.048 1.097-.048 3.233s.009 2.389.047 3.233c.099 2.148 1.106 3.18 3.279 3.279.843.038 1.097.047 3.233.047 2.137 0 2.39-.008 3.233-.046 2.17-.099 3.18-1.129 3.279-3.279.038-.844.046-1.097.046-3.233s-.008-2.389-.046-3.232c-.099-2.153-1.111-3.182-3.279-3.281zm-3.233 10.62c-2.269 0-4.108-1.839-4.108-4.108 0-2.269 1.84-4.108 4.108-4.108s4.108 1.839 4.108 4.108c0 2.269-1.839 4.108-4.108 4.108zm4.271-7.418c-.53 0-.96-.43-.96-.96s.43-.96.96-.96.96.43.96.96-.43.96-.96.96zm-1.604 3.31c0 1.473-1.194 2.667-2.667 2.667s-2.667-1.194-2.667-2.667c0-1.473 1.194-2.667 2.667-2.667s2.667 1.194 2.667 2.667zm4.333-12h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5v-14c0-2.761-2.238-5-5-5zm.952 15.298c-.132 2.909-1.751 4.521-4.653 4.654-.854.039-1.126.048-3.299.048s-2.444-.009-3.298-.048c-2.908-.133-4.52-1.748-4.654-4.654-.039-.853-.048-1.125-.048-3.298 0-2.172.009-2.445.048-3.298.134-2.908 1.748-4.521 4.654-4.653.854-.04 1.125-.049 3.298-.049s2.445.009 3.299.048c2.908.133 4.523 1.751 4.653 4.653.039.854.048 1.127.048 3.299 0 2.173-.009 2.445-.048 3.298z"/>
                </svg>
            </a>
    
            <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/elvisfinol/" target="_blank" class="flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto px-6 py-3 bg-gray-200 text-black font-semibold rounded-lg shadow hover:bg-orange-400 transition duration-300">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M19 0h-14c-2.761 0-5 2.239-5 5v14c0 2.761 2.239 5 5 5h14c2.762 0 5-2.239 5-5V5c0-2.761-2.239-5-5-5zm-11 19H5V8h3v11zM6.5 6.732c-.966 0-1.75-.79-1.75-1.764s.784-1.764 1.75-1.764 1.75.79 1.75 1.764-.783 1.764-1.75 1.764zM19 19h-3v-5.604c0-3.368-4-3.113-4 0V19h-3V8h3v1.765c1.396-2.586 7-2.777 7 2.476V19z"/>
                </svg>
            </a>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-5">
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold">Get to know me!</h1>
            <p>
                Hey there! I’m Elvis, born and raised in the sunny city of Maracaibo,<span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 via-blue-500 to-red-500 
                bg-clip-text text-transparent">Venezuela.</span> 
                Ever since I was a kid, I’ve been the go-to tech handyman for my family. If a computer crashed or needed a reformat, guess who got the call? Yep, 
                that was me! But instead of taking the straight-up tech route, I decided to level up and dive into Electronic Engineering with a focus on Automation and 
                Control Processes at
                <a 
                    href="https://www.urbe.edu/" 
                    target="_blank" 
                    class="text-black font-bold"
                >
                Rafael Belloso Chacín University.
                </a>
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-xl font-bold">My Career Journey 🚀</h1>
            <p>
                From early on, I dreamed of exploring the world, hopping between countries, and soaking up new cultures. So, at 24, 
                I took a leap of faith and packed my bags for Buenos Aires, Argentina. And let me tell you, it’s been quite the ride!
            <p>In Buenos Aires, I kicked off my tech career with
                <a 
                href="https://www.urbe.edu/" 
                    target="_blank"
                    rel="noopener noreferrer"  
                    class="bg-[#06b6d4]/20 text-black font-bold px-1 rounded hover:bg-[#06b6d4]/50 transition duration-200"
                >
                Thomson Reuters Corporation,
                </a>where I provided technical support for their fintech products. 
                That’s when I got hooked on the fascinating world of fintech. After a couple of years, I leveled up and joined
                <a 
                href="https://www.teradata.com/"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                class="bg-[#06b6d4]/20 text-black font-bold px-1 rounded hover:bg-[#06b6d4]/50 transition duration-200"
                >Teradata
                </a>,
                    a big player in database analytics and big data.</p>
                </p>
                <h1 class="text-xl font-bold">Fast Forward to Madrid 🇪🇸</h1>
                <p>
                    Always on the lookout for new adventures, I decided to switch gears and made my way to Madrid, Spain, where I’m currently based. Today, I’m at 
                    <a 
                    href="https://paloaltonetworks.com" 
                    target="_blank" 
                    rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                    class="bg-[#06b6d4]/20 text-black font-bold px-1 rounded hover:bg-[#06b6d4]/50 transition duration-200"
                    >
                    Palo Alto Networks.
                    </a>
                    as a Designated Support Engineer for the EMEA region. My job? I collaborate closely with customers to secure their public 
                    cloud environments, using Prisma Cloud! 😶‍🌫️
                </p>
                <p>So, that’s me in a nutshell! I’m all about embracing new challenges and never settling down.</p>
                <p>But that’s not all—curious about my creative side? Just click
                    <a class="rounded-xl text-black font-semibold transition duration-300 hover:underline" href="/side-hustle">here!</a>
                </p>
        </div>

        <Separator />        

        <div class="">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-orange-500 mb-6">Skill Set & Technologies</h3>
            <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-1">
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Cloud Providers</span> GCP, AWS, Azure</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Cloud-Native Security</span> CNAPP (Prisma Cloud)</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Infrastructure as Code</span> Terraform, CloudFormation</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Containers</span> Docker, Podman</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Container Orchestration</span> GKE, EKS, AKS, AWS ECS, Fargate</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Serverless</span> AWS Lambda, Azure Functions, GCP Functions</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Provisioning</span> CloudFormation, Terraform</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Scripting</span> Bash</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">CI/CD Tools</span> Jenkins, GitHub Actions</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Version Control</span> GitHub</li>
                <li><span class="font-semibold">Logs Management</span> Splunk</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- <Separator />

        <div>
            <h1>Side hustle</h1>
        </div> -->


        <Separator />

        <div class="space-y-5">
            <p class="font-bold">🚀 Let’s Collaborate!</p>
            <!-- <p class="text-base lg:text-lg">Whether it’s scaling your cloud, automating infrastructure, or securing your digital space—I’m here to help.</p> -->
            <p class="text-orange-500 font-semibold">Feel free to reach out via  
                <a href="mailto:e.finol7@gmail.com" class="text-black hover:underline">email</a>, and let’s build something great together! 📩
            </p>
        </div>


    </section>



    
</Layout>

